data.description: Indulge in this luxurious 55+ resort-style living at Trilogy, Tehaleh! This 2-bed, 2.5-bath haven offers 2,181sqft of elegance, backs to a private greenbelt w/access to 30+ miles of trails. Open concept includes a bonus space, guest bed w/ensuite. Kitchen boasts oversized island, SS appliances, cafe' gas 6 burner stove & microwave, and slab quartz countertops. Natural light fills every corner. Primary bedroom is a sanctuary w/ spa-like ensuite & custom walk-in closet. An expansive patio for entertaining. Say goodbye to yard work and hello to a worry-free outdoor haven. Trilogy provides more than a home; it's a lifestyle. Amenities include a pool, exercise room, pickleball, and an onsite restaurant. Elevate your living experience at Trilogy!
